{"tid":831001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】男 子 中 大 天 台 墮 樓 亡","createTime":"2018-09-21T14:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T15:11:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"23bd823ddb43783c3aea4d932e3a8c1ed7271d2f","tid":831001,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180921/large/1537540870_531a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180921%2Flarge%2F1537540870_531a.jpg&h=9be5d045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大晚上發生墮樓案！晚上7時許，警方接報一名年約20歲的男子，於中文大學一校舍的天台危坐，企圖跳樓，其後墮下重傷昏迷，送院搶救後不治，警方正於現場進行調查。<br />\n《蘋果》正就事件向中大查詢。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"060556c9f4d145f5cacf384ef934ad77e85446f6","tid":831001,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"熱門有mmw同埋賤標"},{"pid":"72aa176d062bea93b4619cb0b5ea6c5856e29ff4","tid":831001,"uid":45644,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"年經..."},{"pid":"79ad2f663a645938dd039000b7ca0f7db806f91c","tid":831001,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3f2e1566c5a2193d701b99d8e7b42d7d2a949e2","tid":831001,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"崇基"},{"pid":"821348b8f239ebaa00b1bd65c9670953ec496e8f","tid":831001,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"又有教授用重力殺人？"},{"pid":"7477a2fc6ba4720164de30d659a7e380c06648d7","tid":831001,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:01:30.000Z","ms